\[\begin{aligned}
f_{X_1, X_2}(x_1, x_2) &= 
\begin{cases}
    c(1 - x_2) & 0 \leq x_1 \leq x_2 \leq 1 \\
    0 & \text{otherwise}
\end{cases}
\end{aligned}\]
where $c$ is a constant such that $f_{X_1, X_2}$ is a valid joint pdf. Compute $\text{Cov}(X_1, X_2)$.

